sequenceDiagram
autonumber
participant Dev as Developer
participant GH as GitHub Actions
participant Runner as Runner
participant Repo as Repo

Dev->>GH: triggers "Generate SVG index" (push, workflow_dispatch)
GH->>Runner: dispatch workflow run
Runner->>Repo: checkout (if configured)

Note over Runner: job build-index\nruns-on: ubuntu-latest
Runner->>Runner: uses actions/checkout@v4
Runner->>Repo: git checkout

Runner->>Runner: uses actions/setup-node@v4

Runner->>Runner: Generate index.json

Runner->>Runner: Commit changes (if any)

Runner-->>GH: job "build-index" complete

GH-->>Dev: workflow finished (success/fail)
